<text xml:lang="ta" type="edition">
  <body>
    <div rend="parallel">
      <lg xml:id="ITA67">
<l>kaṇṭēṉ ṟirumēṉi yāṉkaṉavi lāṅkavaṉkaik</l>
<l>kaṇṭēṉ kaṉaluñ cuṭarāḻi – kaṇṭē</l>
<l>ṉuṟunōy viṉaiyiraṇṭu mōṭṭuvittup piṉṉu</l>
<l>maṟunōy ceṟuvāṉ vali</l>
      </lg>
      <lg xml:lang="en">
<l>I saw the holy body in a dream. There, in his hand</l>
<l>I saw the flaming, glowing discus. I saw</l>
<l>the strength of him who drives away pain [already] experienced [and] the two [kinds of] karma</l>
<l>[and] who moreover blocks further pain.</l>
      </lg>
    </div>
